Menu Action Sentence
The Action text is the sentence to be executed for the menu option.  This may
be any sentence that could be executed from the command prompt and may include
inline prompts.

Terminate the action text with a semicolon to cause the menu processor to
issue a "Press return to continue" prompt when the command has completed.

A menu text item that has no associated Action is treated as a sub-heading and
is displayed aligned with the option numbers
